cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.PL

This paper deals with the synthesis of distributed controllers from Petri games, which is a topic related to logic and verification (cs.LO), as well as distributed systems (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the implementation of a tool (ADAM) for this purpose, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
